BR18 uses function-based requirements, references DS/ISO 21542 as voluntary. No specific luminance contrast numbers in the code. Belægningsskift (surface change) in color and tactility required at stairs but qualitative.','2026-05-09 05:35','session_2026-05-09-search-coverage','2026-05-10T19:40:00Z','session_2026-05-10c-protocol-redo.md');
