Accessibility Decree 241/2017 focuses on dimensional requirements. No numerical luminance contrast thresholds found. SFS standards referenced for emergency lighting luminance but not built environment contrast.','2026-05-09 05:35','session_2026-05-09-search-coverage','2026-05-10T19:40:00Z','session_2026-05-10c-protocol-redo.md');
