Boverket BBR recommends NCS lightness contrast ≥0.40 for contrast markings. Uses NCS (Natural Color System) — yet another measurement system distinct from LRV, Michelson, or simple ratio. Guidance, not mandatory.','2026-05-09 05:35','session_2026-05-09-search-coverage','2026-05-10T19:40:00Z','session_2026-05-10c-protocol-redo.md');
