BBL has no specific luminance contrast numbers. NEN 9120 (Feb 2025, voluntary) references NEN-EN 17210 European standard. Qualitative at regulatory level. Practical guidance mentions contrast for markings without numerical thresholds.','2026-05-09 05:35','session_2026-05-09-search-coverage','2026-05-10T19:40:00Z','session_2026-05-10c-protocol-redo.md');
